body:
Hey everyone, my name is Daniel! I&#039;ve been playing League for about 5-6 years, and I&#039;ve always been fascinated by the care that goes into creating and tailoring the lore of each character. I&#039;m currently in my second year of university at Mcgill, and my passion for creative writing and world-building has never been stronger. If there&#039;s an opportunity over the late spring and summer of 2018, I would love to be a part of the process Riot goes through when introducing new lore/elements into the game. Unfortunately, I just don&#039;t know who to get in touch with to get more information. Would someone mind pointing me in the right direction? 

Thanks a bunch!
{{sticker:sg-ezreal}}

replies.body:
